    { question: "What exactly is AI Google Business Profile optimization for electricians?", answer: "It\'s an AI-powered service that manages and grows your Google Business Profile to win more local electrical work. When a homeowner or landlord searches \'electrician near me\', \'EICR near me\', or \'consumer unit upgrade\', Google shows a Maps pack of three local results. Those three listings receive the overwhelming majority of calls. AI optimization positions your electrical business to be one of them. The AI handles three core functions: first, it audits and rebuilds your profile with electrical-specific service categories, accreditation badges, and search-optimised descriptions. Second, it automatically requests Google reviews from your customers via SMS or WhatsApp after every completed job. Third, it responds to reviews and maintains the profile engagement that Google\'s algorithm rewards with higher visibility. The system runs autonomously in the background — you focus on rewires and consumer units while the AI builds your reputation online." },
